data.title: Helgoland-Düne Airport (HGL) in Helgoland, Germany
data.meta_description: Create, visualize, track and map your flights from Helgoland-Düne Airport using our flight mapper. It lies in Helgoland, Germany and has the IATA code of (HGL)
data.text: Heligoland Airport is an airfield on the German island of Düne, the smaller of the two isles of the Heligoland archipelago in the North Sea, about 70 kilometres (43 mi) from the mainland.
